# Data (Raw data is tracked, processed is generated)
# Note: Adjust based on specific data governance policy.
# data/raw/ should ideally be gitignored if large, but kept if small enough.
# For now, ignoring processed outputs which are generated.
data/processed/*
!data/processed/.gitkeep
state/projects/*
!state/projects/.gitkeep
figures/*
!figures/.gitkeep

